OL,3,C7m hours collectively spent waiting to
OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FCustomers spent 798 years collectively
OL,8,Fwaiting to speak with HM Revenue and
OL,9,FCustoms (HMRC) in 2022-23 ` more than
OL,10,Fdouble the time spent waiting in 2019-
OL,11,F20, according to a spending watchdog.
OL,13,FThe equivalent of 798 years ` or
OL,14,Faround seven million hours ` was spent
OL,15,Fby customers and their agents waiting
OL,16,Fto speak to an adviser in 2022-23, up
OL,17,Ffrom 365 years or around 3.2 million
OL,18,Fhours in 2019-20.
