OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHMRC's strategy is to encourage
OL,8,Fcustomers to turn to its digital
OL,9,Fservices first ` but it is not clear
OL,10,Fhow far and fast digital services will
OL,11,Freduce demand for telephone and
OL,12,Fcorrespondence services, the National
OL,13,FAudit Office (NAO) said.
OL,15,FThe strategy is intended to cut costs
OL,16,Fservicing telephone calls and
OL,17,Fcorrespondence, as well as to free up
OL,18,Fstaff to serve people who need extra
OL,19,Fsupport.
