OL,3,C7m hours collectively spent waiting to
OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe NAO said that HMRC has not yet
OL,8,Fdone enough to raise awareness of its
OL,9,Fdigital services, increase customers'
OL,10,Fconfidence in using its online
OL,11,Foffering or understand how effectively
OL,12,Fthese services meet customers' needs.
OL,14,FIt said the move to digital services
OL,15,Fhas not eased pressure on traditional
OL,16,Fservices as much as HMRC expected `
OL,17,Fand many avoidable customer calls are
OL,18,Fcaused by the revenue body itself for
OL,19,Freasons including delays and customers
OL,20,Fchasing progress.
