OL,3,C7m hours collectively spent waiting to
OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FSome 4.7 million hours was spent by
OL,8,FHMRC customer service advisers
OL,9,Fanswering and handling calls in 2022-
OL,10,F23, down from 5.0 million in 2019-20.
OL,12,FAdvisers answered 22% fewer calls in
OL,13,F2022-23 than in 2019-20, but those
OL,14,Fthat were answered took more time to
OL,15,Fhandle on average.
OL,17,FThe time taken to handle each call
OL,18,Fanswered by an adviser increased from
OL,19,Fjust over 11 minutes in 2019-20 to
OL,20,Fmore than 13 minutes in 2022-23.
