OL,3,C7m hours collectively spent waiting to
OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAverage call-handling time may be
OL,8,Fincreasing because more simple queries
OL,9,Fare being handled digitally; call-
OL,10,Fhandling efficiency is reducing; or
OL,11,Fcustomers are raising more issues when
OL,12,Fthey are able to get through to an
OL,13,Fadviser, the report said.
OL,15,FSome taxpayers hold multiple jobs,
OL,16,Fmeaning they have less straightforward
OL,17,Fneeds, while "fiscal drag", where
OL,18,Fpeople are pushed over frozen tax
OL,19,Fthresholds by pay rises, has also
OL,20,Fbrought more people into the tax
OL,21,Fsystem.
