OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FWith HMRC's call-handling workload
OL,8,Ffalling less than expected, it has not
OL,9,Fbeen able to make all the staff
OL,10,Freductions it planned, the NAO said.
OL,12,FIn March 2024, HMRC announced that it
OL,13,Fwould restrict helplines, its self-
OL,14,Fassessment helpline. It reversed its
OL,15,Fdecision a day later following an
OL,16,Foutcry from a range of organisations.
