OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe department had trialled closing
OL,8,Fand restricting helplines in 2023 but
OL,9,Fthe NAO said its evaluation of the
OL,10,Fchanges did not consider stakeholder
OL,11,Fviews or adequately assess the impacts
OL,12,Fof the changes on customers.
OL,14,FHMRC had expected that closing the
OL,15,Fhelplines would free up around 520
OL,16,Fmembers of staff to work on other
OL,17,Fhelplines and tackle processing
OL,18,Fbacklogs.
