OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe NAO report said: "HMRC's telephone
OL,8,Fand correspondence services have been
OL,9,Ffalling below the expected service
OL,10,Flevels for too long and HMRC has not
OL,11,Fachieved planned efficiencies."
OL,13,FIt said HMRC should develop more
OL,14,Frealistic plans for cutting the
OL,15,Fservices it is replacing with digital
OL,16,Fchannels.
