OL,7,FOn Monday this week, the Treasury
OL,8,Fannounced #51 million in additional
OL,9,Ffunding so that staff can answer more
OL,10,Fcalls and help more people on the
OL,11,Fphone.
OL,13,FAnnouncing the funding, financial
OL,14,Fsecretary to the Treasury Nigel
OL,15,FHuddleston said on Monday that he is
OL,16,F"fully committed" to providing HMRC
OL,17,Fwith the resources to meet customer
OL,18,Fneeds.
