OL,3,C7m hours collectively spent waiting to
OL,4,Cspeak to taxman in 2022-23, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,8,F"HMRC's telephone and correspondence
OL,9,Fservices have been below its target
OL,10,Fservice levels for too long.
OL,12,F"While many of its digital services
OL,13,Fwork well, they have not made enough
OL,14,Fof a difference to customers, some of
OL,15,Fwhom have been caught in a declining
OL,16,Fspiral of service pressures and cuts.
OL,17,FHMRC has also not achieved planned
OL,18,Fefficiencies.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
