OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAn HMRC spokesperson said: "While
OL,8,Fcustomer service standards on our
OL,9,Fphone lines are still not where we
OL,10,Fwant them to be, we're making strong
OL,11,Fprogress in our efforts to improve our
OL,12,Fcustomer service and additional
OL,13,Ffunding has been confirmed by the
OL,14,FGovernment this week.
OL,16,F"Millions more people used our highly-
OL,17,Frated online services last year `
OL,18,Fsaving them waiting on the phone and
OL,19,Ffreeing up our advisers to deal with
OL,20,Fthose people who need extra support.
