OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"We continue to encourage people to
OL,8,Fdeal with us online or via the app
OL,9,Fwhere they can and we are working to
OL,10,Fprovide even better, easier and always-
OL,11,Favailable online services. But, as we
OL,12,Fhave recognised, these changes need to
OL,13,Fhappen at a speed and in ways that our
OL,14,Fcustomers are comfortable with."
OL,16,FJohn O'Connell, chief executive of the
OL,17,FTaxPayers' Alliance, said: "This
OL,18,Fscathing report from the NAO will come
OL,19,Fas no surprise to taxpayers who have
OL,20,Ftried and tried again to contact HMRC."
