OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FDame Harriett Baldwin, chairwoman of
OL,8,Fthe Treasury Committee, said:
OL,9,F"Unfortunately, the NAO's findings
OL,10,Fcome as no surprise. For a long time,
OL,11,Fthe Treasury Committee has been
OL,12,Fbanging the drum for a more coherent
OL,13,Fcommunications plan from HMRC on their
OL,14,Fplans to move customers online.
OL,16,F"The committee broadly supports the
OL,17,Fdepartment's plans but they must take
OL,18,Flaw-abiding taxpayers with them ` and
OL,19,Fthat simply hasn't happened yet.
