OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"The committee has repeatedly
OL,8,Fdiscussed low service standards with
OL,9,FHMRC so we are pleased the Government
OL,10,Flistened to our plea not to further
OL,11,Freduce the capacity of the phone lines
OL,12,Fthis year. The extra money announced
OL,13,Fby the Treasury this week to keep
OL,14,Fphone lines going is welcome, but
OL,15,Fquestions remain regarding how they
OL,16,Fplan to implement their strategy going
OL,17,Fforward."
