OL,7,FShadow Treasury minister James Murray
OL,8,Fsaid: "As businesses and taxpayers
OL,9,Facross the country already know,
OL,10,Fservice levels at HMRC ` like so many
OL,11,Fother public services ` have been
OL,12,Fcollapsing under the Conservatives.
OL,14,F"It is staggering that taxpayers spent
OL,15,Fnearly 800 years in total waiting on
OL,16,Fhold for HMRC. That is double the
OL,17,Famount of time at the last election,
OL,18,Fand shows the Conservatives have no
OL,19,Fidea how to deliver the service that
OL,20,Fpeople deserve."
